=head1 DESCRIPTION

Contains details about the OpenAPI schema for a custom plugin. For more
information, see custom plugin OpenAPI schemas
(https://docs.aws.amazon.com/amazonq/latest/qbusiness-ug/custom-plugin.html#plugins-api-schema).
You can either include the schema directly in the payload field or you
can upload it to an S3 bucket and specify the S3 bucket location in the
C<s3> field.

=head1 ATTRIBUTES


=head2 Payload => Str

The JSON or YAML-formatted payload defining the OpenAPI schema for a
custom plugin.


=head2 S3 => L<Paws::QBusiness::S3>

Contains details about the S3 object containing the OpenAPI schema for
a custom plugin. The schema could be in either JSON or YAML format.



